flowchart TD
    subgraph A[Input Layer: In-Vehicle Networks]
        CAN[Controller Area Network<br>CAN Bus Traffic]
        Eth[Automotive Ethernet<br>Ethernet Frames & SOME/IP]
    end

    subgraph B[Protocol-Specific Feature Extraction]
        CAN --> P1[Can Feature Extractor<br>Time-Series Features<br>e.g., ID Frequency, Payload Entropy]
        Eth --> P2[Ethernet Feature Extractor<br>Spatial-Temporal Features<br>e.g., Image Transform WT, Packet Sequences]
    end

    subgraph C[Cross-Protocol Correlation & Fusion Core]
        P1 --> Correlation[Cross-Protocol<br>Correlation Engine]
        P2 --> Correlation
        Correlation --> Fusion[Feature Fusion Layer]
    end

    subgraph D[Tiered Detection & Decision]
        Fusion --> LightweightModel[Lightweight Detection Tier<br>e.g., Distilled CNN-BiLSTM<br><500KB, <1ms]
        LightweightModel --> Decision{Confidence Threshold}
        Decision -- "High Confidence<br>(Attack/Normal)" --> Alert
        Decision -- "Low Confidence /<br>Complex Pattern" --> HeavyModel[Heavy Analysis Tier<br>e.g., Full Attention-Based Model<br>On Gateway/Cloud]
        HeavyModel --> Alert[Final Intrusion<br>Alert & Log]
    end

    subgraph E[Validation & Output]
        Alert --> Metrics[Performance Metrics:<br>F1-Score, Latency, Model Size]
    end